{"title":"为了祖国（外一首）","authors":["石太瑞"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":10,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石太瑞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人要是能活上一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国啊我愿为你活上一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人要是能死去一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国啊我愿为你死去一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我活上一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是要为你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多背运一次砖石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多耕耘一次土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多演算一道难题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你的繁荣而繁荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我死去一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是要为你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多抛洒一次热血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多抗击一次灾难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多扑灭一次战火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你的神圣而神圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然不能活上一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然不能死去一千次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你的美好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你的尊严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一次我也足够了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一次是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你而死为你而生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最激动我的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当然是《国歌》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有它能使十二亿人的泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为笑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的站起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不是1937年的站起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不是1937年的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时面对最危险的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但只要唱起它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们便感到最为安全"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}